data.name: Creamy Avocado Toast with Roasted Veggies
data.quickTastyDescription: A delightful combination of creamy avocado and savory roasted vegetables on toasted bread, perfect for a quick meal or snack.
detailedCookingInstructions: On a baking sheet, toss the diced bell pepper, zucchini, and cherry tomatoes with olive oil, salt, black pepper, and garlic powder.
Spread the veggies in a single layer and roast in the oven for about 15-20 minutes, until tender and slightly caramelized.
While the veggies are roasting, toast the whole grain bread until golden brown.
Mash the ripe avocado in a bowl and season with salt and red pepper flakes if desired.
Spread the mashed avocado generously over the toasted bread.
Once the veggies are done, top the avocado toast with the roasted vegetables and serve immediately.
data.detailedName: Creamy Avocado Toast with Roasted Veggies
data.modifiersForBase: Adding roasted vegetables for extra flavor and nutrients
